overview: There's never any hazing at CF; our freshman are always welcomed right into the fold by our upperclassman, and in this fourth volume of our fresh-faced freshmen we're happy to present Justin, Wesley, Levi, and Tevin in four more of our hottest jock-on-twink scenes. These boys really come out of their shells when our hunky upperclassmen put them through their paces! Our young, inexperienced freshmen are fast learners when it comes to taking big cocks in every position imaginable and they're eager to show you that they keep up just as well as our veterans.
title: Fresh-Faced Freshmen 4
